author: The Piano Guys
description:
For our first release of 2025, check out our cover of “Test Drive” from How to Train Your Dragon! We couldn’t be more excited to kick off the year with a cinematic tribute to one of our favorite stories.🐉🎶
Stream at the link in our bio! 

 The new How to Train Your Dragon movie is out today! If you’re planning to see it, drop the word “dragon” in the comments!
title: How to Train Your Dragon Out Now

“Once there were dragons…”
We’ve always been inspired by the epic storytelling and breathtaking score of How to Train Your Dragon. This cover of “Test Drive” is our tribute to the powerful bond between Hiccup and Toothless and the soaring spirit of adventure that defines this beloved film.
